OL,3,CSchools should be phone-free zones,
OL,4,Ceducation secretary tells headteachers
OL,6,FLast week, the government issued
OL,7,Fupdated guidance around phone use in
OL,8,Fschools, stressing pupils "should not
OL,9,Fhave access to their devices during
OL,10,Flessons, break times, lunch times, or
OL,11,Fbetween lessons".
OL,13,FThe Department for Science, Innovation
OL,14,Fand Technology (DSIT) said it will
OL,15,Falso be taking immediate action on
OL,16,Fchildren's social media use, including
OL,17,Fdirecting Ofsted to examine schools'
OL,18,Fmobile phone policies and how
OL,19,Feffectively they are implemented
OL,20,Fduring inspections.
