OL,3,CSchools should be phone-free zones,
OL,4,Ceducation secretary tells headteachers
OL,6,F"I have always been clear that mobile
OL,7,Fphones have no place in schools - I
OL,8,Fknow many of you feel the same,"
OL,9,Fwrites the education secretary.
OL,11,F"It is clear that the previous
OL,12,Fguidance did not deliver the clarity
OL,13,For consistency that schools need, or
OL,14,Fhelp enough in setting out for parents
OL,15,Fthat this is a clear national position.
