OL,3,CSchools should be phone-free zones,
OL,4,Ceducation secretary tells headteachers
OL,6,F"That is why we have strengthened it
OL,7,Fto be explicit - all schools should be
OL,8,Fphone-free environments for the entire
OL,9,Fschool day. That includes lessons,
OL,10,Ftime between lessons, breaktimes and
OL,11,Flunchtime."
OL,13,FPhillipson went on to stress that
OL,14,F"Ofsted will, for the first time,
OL,15,Fexamine both schools' mobile phone
OL,16,Fpolicies and how effectively they are
OL,17,Fapplied when judging behaviour during
OL,18,Finspections."
OL,20,FTeachers have also been advised not to
OL,21,Fuse their phones in front of pupils.
