OL,6,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,7,Fthe National Association of Head
OL,8,FTeachers, told the BBC that school
OL,9,Fleaders "need support from government,
OL,10,Fnot the threat of heavy-handed
OL,11,Finspection".
