OL,3,CSchools should be phone-free zones,
OL,4,Ceducation secretary tells headteachers
OL,6,FThe consultation will look at options
OL,7,Fincluding raising the digital age of
OL,8,Fconsent and restricting potentially
OL,9,Faddictive app design features such as
OL,10,F"streaks" and "infinite scrolling".
OL,12,FMinisters will visit Australia as part
OL,13,Fof the consultation, where a social
OL,14,Fmedia ban for under-16s came into
OL,15,Fforce in December.
OL,17,FThe government will seek views from
OL,18,Fparents and young people and will
OL,19,Frespond in the summer, DSIT said.
